- Evaluation criteria (homogeneity, contiguity, size): [Context: SSW, PctML, Wu & Murray metric]
- Algorithm performance: [Context: HSSC outperforms others in 2/3 criteria; Complete-link/UPGMA best for PctML; Ward's lowest for contiguity]
- Trade-offs and application needs: [Context: “trade-off between landscape homogeneity and spatial contiguity”]

